modName: Snow Elf Brother Pack -Dawnguard NOT Required
summary: Adds three Snow Elf followers to the Thieves Guild\'s Headquarters.
descriptionHtml:
*DAWNGUARD NOT REQUIRED* 
Three Snow elf twins (not 100% identical). You can marry each one, and each one is an essential follower (will not die). 
I made this with the thought to bring snow elves to those of us who haven\'t purchased Dawnguard. 
I will upgrade them soon, giving each individual a separate bonus to you. 

Enjoy!
author: Kolton Burke
